dc.title: USFWS: Welcome to our Fisheries and Habitat Conservation Web Site!
dc.description: Home page of the U.S. Fish and Wildlife Service, Fisheries and Habitat Conservation Program. Our mission is to provide leadership in sustaining and enhancing fish, wildlife, and their habitats for the benefit of the American people and to engage citizens in the shared stewardship of our Nation's natural resources.
